{"version":1,"entries":{"person_76944_translations":{"at":1772647161756,"data":{"id":76944,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Maxine Peake (born 14 July 1974) is an English stage, radio, film and television actress, playwright, producer, director and political activist, who made her name as Twinkle in Victoria Wood's sitcom Dinnerladies. She has since played Veronica in Channel 4's Manchester-based drama series Shameless, barrister Martha Costello in the BBC legal drama Silk and Grace Middleton in The Village. She is also an accomplished stage actress, having played the title role in Hamlet, and had a role in the 2014 film The Theory of Everything. In 2018 she played the lead in the film Funny Cow and had a starring role in Mike Leigh's epic Peterloo, a film very close to her heart.","name":"Maxine Peake","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"玛克辛·皮克（Maxine Peake，1974年7月14日-）是一位英国舞台、广播、电影和电视女演员、剧作家、制片人、导演和政治活动家，她在维多利亚·伍德的情景喜剧《晚餐女士》中饰演Twinkle。此后，她在第 4 频道的曼彻斯特电视剧《无耻之徒》中扮演维罗妮卡，在 BBC 法律剧《丝绸》中扮演大律师玛莎·科斯特洛，在《村庄》中扮演格蕾丝·米德尔顿。她也是一位多才多艺的舞台女演员，曾在《哈姆雷特》中扮演主角，并在 2014 年的电影《万物理论》中扮演角色。2018 年，她在电影《滑稽牛》中担任主角，并在迈克·利的史诗《彼得卢》中担任主演，这部电影非常贴近她的内心。","name":"玛克辛·皮克","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"맥신 피크","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"瑪克辛·皮克（Maxine Peake，1974 年 7 月 14 日-）是一位英國舞台、廣播、電影和電視女演員、劇作家、製片人、導演和政治活動家，她在維多利亞·伍德的情景喜劇《晚餐女士》中飾演 Twinkle。此後，她在第 4 頻道的曼徹斯特電視劇《無恥之徒》中扮演維羅妮卡，在 BBC 法律劇《絲綢》中扮演大律師瑪莎·科斯特洛，在《村莊》中扮演格蕾絲·米德爾頓。她也是一位多才多藝的舞台女演員，曾在《王子復仇記》中扮演主角，並在 2014 年的電影《霍金：愛的方程式》中扮演角色。2018 年，她在電影《滑稽牛》中擔任主角，並在邁克·利的史詩《彼得盧》中擔任主演，這部電影非常貼近她的內心。","name":"瑪克辛·皮克","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Максін Пік","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Максин Пик","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"マキシン・ピーク","primary":false}}]}},"person_2886486_translations":{"at":1772647167178,"data":{"id":2886486,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Levon Panek attended Bentley University in Waltham, MA, where he majored in managerial economics and minored in quantitative perspectives. He took screenwriting as an elective, and coincidentally was taught by legendary acting coach, Gerry Speca, who two decades prior had taught both Ben and Casey Affleck, as well as Matt Damon, at Cambridge Rindge & Latin. Halfway through the semester Speca approached Panek about acting, alluded to his potential, and told him that he should attend open call auditions. Panek went to an open call for \"The Town\" and was subsequently chosen by casting to portray a bouncer in \"The Social Network.\" After taking a hiatus from acting and working as a strength & conditioning coach, Panek returned to cinema in 2018 and booked two more speaking roles: as the characters Donald in \"Love, Weddings, & Other Disasters,\" and then as State Trooper Dennis in the Showtime series \"Dexter: New Blood,\" before his acting coach told him to pursue stunts as way of expediting his career path as an action actor. In 2022 he did all of the fight scenes as the Big Daddy character in season 11 of \"American Horror Story,\" and had on-screen fights in movies with Liam Neeson, Stephen Lang, and Lucas Till. His most notable TV performance is as the character James 'Goliath' Kenneally in \"Law & Order: Organized Crime,\" season 3, episodes 13 and 14.","name":"Levon Panek","primary":true}}]}},"person_83528_translations":{"at":1772647168862,"data":{"id":83528,"translati