"name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"姜大卫，香港著名导演兼演员。4岁开始登台演出至今，已有将近六十年，而其参演和导演的影视作品总数已超过一百六十部，而且他还在不断的给我们创造新的银幕形象。从演出第一部电影《澳门大血案》开始，接连拍摄了《近水楼台》《江山美人》等片。","name":"姜大卫","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"강대위","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"姜大衛，又名姜大偉，本名姜偉年，尊稱「John 哥」，加拿大籍香港人，香港男演員及導演；曾為麗的電視、亞洲電視及香港電視網絡前藝員，現為無綫電視基本藝人合約藝員，曾於 1970 年《第 16 屆亞洲影展金禾獎》中憑電影《報仇》獲頒「最佳男主角」，後於《萬千星輝頒獎典禮 2021》榮獲「萬千光輝演藝大獎」，及於 2024 年憑電影《白日之下》獲頒第 42 屆香港電影金像獎「最佳男配角」。","name":"姜大衛","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"姜大衛","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"David Chiang","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Khương Đại Vệ","primary":false}}]}},"movie_1327688_keywords":{"at":1772647175468,"data":{"id":1327688,"keywords":[{"id":6158,"name":"cult"},{"id":7312,"name":"road trip"},{"id":240303,"name":"father daughter relationship"},{"id":281237,"name":"independent film"},{"id":324297,"name":"college tour"}]}},"person_3826106_translations":{"at":1772647185069,"data":{"id":3826106,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Natacha Srichai","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"Natacha Srichai","primary":true}}]}},"person_3771219_translations":{"at":1772647187171,"data":{"id":3771219,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Panichadar Sangsuwan","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"ปาณิชดา แสงสุวรรณ","primary":true}}]}},"person_1873038_translations":{"at":1772647188422,"data":{"id":1873038,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"A Hungarian native, Bernadett is a London-based actress, most commonly recognized for her starring role in the Hungarian feature film, PAPPA PIA. She started her international career in a BBC mini-series, FLEMING, portraying Ilsa, who takes revenge on a Nazi officer who killed her family. Bernadett recently appeared in Hong Kong cinemas as Scarlet in the Chinese feature film, SU REN TE GONG. Bernadett studied at the University of Theatre and Film Arts in Budapest, where she was trained by Gabor Zsambeki and Sandor Zsoter. After University, she was an actor in residence for 2 years at Vororsmarty Theatre, one of Hungary's most ambitious theatres with over 140 years of history. Bernadett walked the stage as a lead in several dramas, comedies and musicals. Outside of Vorosmarty Theatre, she starred in THE CLEARING at the Szkene Theatre, which won the ‘Best Independent Play’ Critics’ Award in 2014. Bernadett won't flinch at diving 40 meters underwater, among sharks and octopi, but do not force her to have breakfast outside in the summer--she’s desperately scared of wasps!","name":"Bernadett Ostorházi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HU","iso_639_1":"hu","name":"Magyar","english_name":"Hungarian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Bernadett Ostorházi","primary":true}}]}},"person_238193_translations":{"at":1772647191312,"data":{"id":238193,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Artika Sari Devi (born September 29, 1979) is an Indonesian actress, music producer, model and beauty pageant titleholder who the winner of Puteri Indonesia 2004 (Miss Universe Indonesia), She also representing Indonesia in 2005 Miss Universe pa